house-pelletierdefontenay-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe designers expand by saying: “The stepped configuration of the ground floor also helped lower the building’s overall footprint, while creating a natural airflow between the spaces towards the upper level. In the summer, this helps to naturally ventilate the common spaces, while in winter, the warm air is captured and redistributed through the house via the high-efficiency heat recovery mechanical system.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570297\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570297\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-pelletierdefontenay-8-810x549.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist interior with light wooden flooring, white walls, a wooden staircase, and a framed landscape painting above a brick fireplace.\" width=\"810\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-pelletierdefontenay-8-810x549.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-pelletierdefontenay-8-800x543.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-pelletierdefontenay-8-768x521.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-pelletierdefontenay-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570296\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570296\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-pelletierdefontenay-19-810x550.jpg\" alt=\"Sunlit bedroom with large windows overlooking green trees and a grassy flat roof. Wooden ceiling beams are visible, and a bed is partially in view.\" width=\"810\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/suttonhouse-p